name: Satsviz
tagline: A plugin in QGIS to Connec SatScan with GIS
body:
SaTSViz
=======
Due to change in the QGIS API in QGIS 2.x vesrion, this plugin is broken. We will update you as soon as this plugin get ready for QGIS 2.x. Also currently this plugin can only works with windows installation of SatScan.
I request developers to contribute to this project to make it workable.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
